%T A394755 12971518524320,4978986704302097,3532978161315634913,
%U A394755 4653469892186977002460,11423275400784921191855736,52462085466397337031539370710,452380601683401136290499567383958
%N A394755 Number of connected semi-bipartite structures on n unlabeled vertices.
%C A394755 A semi-bipartite structure is a triple (G,U,V) such that G is a simple graph, U and V form a partition of V[G], and U is isolated in G. a(n) counts non-isomorphic triples (G,U,V) on n unlabeled vertices such that G is connected.
%C A394755 Since U and V form a partition, both must be nonempty. When U or V can be empty, the corresponding sequence is A394610.
%C A394755 When G isn't required to be connected, the corresponding sequence is A394754.
%F A394755 a(n) = A394610(n) - A001349(n) for n>=2.
%e A394755 For n = 3: a(2)=1 with the following structure: two connected vertices with one in U and the other in V.
%Y A394755 Cf. A394610, A001349, A394754.
%K A394755 nonn,new
%O A394755 0,4
%A A394755 _Piotr Mitosek_, Mar 31 2026
